About 1991 I think.

token_lists.title: Data World
token_lists.description:
"DATA WORLD" series are new world structures created from abstract data, designed as a result of visualization of data sets with the help of algorithms.

I calculated the datasets in the automatic random dataset calculator, with 50 rows of random dataset calculated for each DATA WORLD. I visualize the rows containing these datasets with neural networks that I have trained later (neural networks trained with lots of photos)
